title: Shoukan sareta Kenja wa Isekai wo Iku: Saikyou nano wa Fuyou Zaiko no Item deshita
original_name: 召喚された賢者は異世界を往く～最強なのは不要在庫のアイテムでした～
sinopse:
Touya was suddenly summoned to another world while playing a game. Summoned as a game character, he is soon banished from the kingdom because they were seeking a hero, and his character was just a level 1 healer.

(Source: Kadokawa, translated)
